<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.1">
<l>kaḷvaṉkol yāṉaṟiyēṉ kariyāṉoru kāḷaivantu</l>
<l>vaḷḷima ruṅkuleṉṟaṉ maṭamāṉiṉaip pōtaveṉṟu</l>
<l>veḷḷiva ḷaikkaipaṟṟap peṟṟatāyarai viṭṭakaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaḷḷalam pūṅkaḻaṉi yaṇiyālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is he a thief? I don’t know! The dark one, coming [as] a young man</l>
<l>Telling my simple, creeper-waisted doe[-like girl] to come,</l>
<l>Having departed as [he] grabbed her silver-bangled arm,</l>
<l rend="indent">leaving [her] own mother,</l>
<l>Are they setting out for lovely Āli with muddy fields of beautiful blossoms?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
